WEBVTT

00:12.490 --> 00:16.029
I must thank Kingsley for giving such a nice
introduction.

00:16.029 --> 00:25.990
When I went to Australia, people asked me,
are your disciples all scholars?

00:25.990 --> 00:32.390
I said, they come from all walks of life,
there are very few who could really be called

00:32.390 --> 00:43.809
scholars but I think after getting realisation,
you being the complete knowledge, new venues

00:43.809 --> 00:53.680
open within you. You start knowing so many
things, like when you enter in this room and

00:53.680 --> 00:59.430
it is absolutely dark, you can’t see anything.
You don’t know much about it, you don’t

00:59.430 --> 01:07.359
know how to walk, where to walk, you may just
stumble down, but if there is light, you know

01:07.359 --> 01:13.979
so many things suddenly and you are amazed
at yourself that you have come to know so

01:13.979 --> 01:19.359
many things.

01:19.359 --> 01:31.259
Now this knowledge that you have, is not the
knowledge that we read in the books. If I

01:31.259 --> 01:40.329
put my finger to this flame here, it will
burn. Anybody who puts the finger to the flame,

01:40.329 --> 01:54.200
it will burn. Now this knowledge that the
finger has to burn has come to us through

01:54.200 --> 02:04.579
our experience and is built within us. Everybody
gets it without paying for it, without making

02:04.579 --> 02:10.399
any effort for it, it is built in within us.

02:10.399 --> 02:17.340
In the same way, we are so organised within
ourselves, we are made within ourselves so

02:17.340 --> 02:26.030
well that if this happening which he told
you about, the awakening of the kundalini,

02:26.030 --> 02:31.280
if it takes place, it is just like this instrument
being connected to the mains and it starts

02:31.280 --> 02:38.719
working. I mean you are wonderfully made,
no doubt about it and thousands of years,

02:38.719 --> 02:49.159
thousands and thousands and thousands of years
have passed till you become a human being.

02:49.159 --> 03:01.319
This human being, the body, the mind is all
made this way, organised this way for one

03:01.319 --> 03:08.219
purpose, and the one purpose is to become
one with your spirit.

03:08.219 --> 03:19.140
Now, why? why should we become one with our
spirit? Because the spirit is the universal

03:19.140 --> 03:27.980
being within us, is the reflection of God
Almighty, is God reflected within us, in our

03:27.980 --> 03:37.719
heart. That spirit is eternal, it is not destructible,
it is unattached and it is the witness of

03:37.719 --> 03:46.459
our lives. It witnesses what we are doing,
it knows all the fields in which we move but

03:46.459 --> 03:54.139
it is not in our conscious mind. We cannot
feel it, we cannot manoeuvre it, we cannot

03:54.139 --> 03:56.420
understand it’s powers.

03:56.420 --> 04:09.760
So the whole being is created, through a power
of desire. The desire which is very strong,

04:09.760 --> 04:15.819
that you have to become the spirit is still
unmanifested. It is residual and resides in

04:15.819 --> 04:27.039
the triangular bone called sacrum. Sacrum
means sacred. Today on the radio, they asked

04:27.039 --> 04:35.699
me a question, that here the people are so
complicated, do you find it easy to convince

04:35.699 --> 04:45.669
people about God? About Kundalini? They are
very sceptical, is it easy for you to do that?

04:45.669 --> 04:57.069
It’s a very nice question because she could
see my problem. Now I have to tell you one

04:57.069 --> 05:10.090
thing, that this power that resides within
us has been there and many people have talked

05:10.090 --> 05:20.770
about it. It has been there, no doubt about
it, but in modern times we want to know whether

05:20.770 --> 05:30.460
it is there or not. Now there are many people
here who have seen the pulsation of this power

05:30.460 --> 05:36.789
in the triangular bone. They have seen it
and you can also see it, for your conviction,

05:36.789 --> 05:50.360
to see for yourself. But I would suggest that
there is no shop, nothing is selling here.

05:50.360 --> 05:56.770
This kind of sceptical attitude is alright
for people who are going to buy something.

05:56.770 --> 06:05.169
That they want to know whether it is right
or not. Suppose you are entering into a university

06:05.169 --> 06:12.270
and you are there to discover some scientific
knowledge, then do you go with a sceptical

06:12.270 --> 06:25.050
mind? You go with an open mind. You need not
be sceptical and you need not be closed. You

06:25.050 --> 06:30.319
need not be also following anything blindly
that I say. There is no need to have blind

06:30.319 --> 06:36.129
faith in Sahaja Yoga, no need at all. It is
for you to see for yourself if it works out

06:36.129 --> 06:45.729
or not. One should not come with an attitude
that if it does not work out then there is

06:45.729 --> 06:51.439
something wrong about it, maybe there is something
wrong with you, because there is nothing selling

06:51.439 --> 06:57.710
here, it is a gift. It’s a gift of God,
it’s the grace of God because he is anxious

06:57.710 --> 07:03.569
to save this creation. That’s why he is
giving it to you, to masses, it has never

07:03.569 --> 07:04.970
happened before.

07:04.970 --> 07:10.750
This is something so unique that is happening,
I myself am surprised at the way it is working

07:10.750 --> 07:16.189
out. So when all this is happening, why not
benefit by that? It is you who is going to

07:16.189 --> 07:24.849
benefit not me, not at all. When you understand
this, your attitude will be much more positive

07:24.849 --> 07:28.840
towards taking realisation here.

07:28.840 --> 07:33.460
Now human beings are not going to be happy
without their self being discovered, whatever

07:33.460 --> 07:40.580
you may try. You give them money, they become
affluent then they will become hippies as

07:40.580 --> 07:46.270
they become fed up of it. You give them power,
they will fight among themselves or they give

07:46.270 --> 07:51.360
up politics. They will never be satisfied
with all these things because they know it

07:51.360 --> 08:00.490
is not satisfying, why? Because satisfaction
can only be enjoyed by the spirit. Only the

08:00.490 --> 08:07.349
spirit can enjoy. Rest of the enjoyments are
temporary, transitory and they vanish into

08:07.349 --> 08:10.080
thin air.

08:10.080 --> 08:16.479
All complexities of life, all problems of
life that faces you, is because without knowing

08:16.479 --> 08:24.599
the absolute you have gone into relative dimensions.
If you do not know where Brighton is and you

08:24.599 --> 08:31.189
have to go to Brighton, you move about all
over the places and never reach the point.

08:31.189 --> 08:32.790
You will be complicated, no doubt.

08:32.790 --> 08:39.540
First of all you must discover that absolute,
and that has to be, if you don’t do it,

08:39.540 --> 08:50.510
you are going to fail, in life, in satisfaction,
in happiness. But, it’s not only that, it’s

08:50.510 --> 08:58.330
much more because the spirit has all the dynamism
of God’s Divine power which is all pervading,

08:58.330 --> 09:03.170
which is everywhere, you cannot feel it, it
is everywhere. I’ll say it is everywhere,

09:03.170 --> 09:10.780
there is music, drama, you won’t believe
me until I put a television down here. In

09:10.780 --> 09:17.340
the same way unless and until you become one
with yourself, you are not going to feel that

09:17.340 --> 09:26.290
all pervading power, that blissful power of
God because you are not yet there.

09:26.290 --> 09:32.080
You have to enter into the kingdom of God.
Now there is another objection that always

09:32.080 --> 09:38.880
comes in because people are very much Christian
minded and they want to ask me one question

09:38.880 --> 09:45.520
which I have been wanting to answer many a
time. They said that we can only reach God

09:45.520 --> 09:53.220
through Christ. Yes, that’s true but how?
Where is Christ? Where is he? Do they know

09:53.220 --> 09:57.580
where does he exist? Are we going to pierce
through his body? Where is his body? Where

09:57.580 --> 09:59.380
do you find him?

09:59.380 --> 10:03.670
He was crucified a long time back, he is no
more. He is not in the churches, of this be

10:03.670 --> 10:07.940
assured and he is not with the priests at
all, then where is he?

10:07.940 --> 10:14.470
He is within us, now where is he within us?
No one knows about it, he exists within us.

10:14.470 --> 10:21.760
I say he exists where? You see this red mark?
Behind that is a centre called agnya chakra,

10:21.760 --> 10:28.070
he resides there. You have to enter through
that door of Christ, you have to awaken them.

10:28.070 --> 10:32.190
Unless and until you awaken Christ, you cannot
enter the kingdom of God.

10:32.190 --> 10:39.040
(Mother asks a yogi if they have the chart
so she could have shown the exact location

10:39.040 --> 10:40.440
of the kingdom of God)

10:40.440 --> 10:47.590
The kingdom of God is the limbic area and
to enter into it, you have to pass through

10:47.590 --> 10:53.310
this very subtle centre which is placed in
the centre of the optic chiasma, the centre

10:53.310 --> 10:56.420
governs the pituitary and the pineal body.

10:56.420 --> 11:02.970
You have to cross through that. What is it
to cross? What are you? You are your attention.

11:02.970 --> 11:09.650
Your attention has to pass through that and
awaken that centre. When you awaken that centre,

11:09.650 --> 11:16.260
Christ is awakened within you and your ego
and superego, your karmas, so called, your

11:16.260 --> 11:20.600
sins, so called, all are sucked.

11:20.600 --> 11:26.380
You come into that area called the limbic
area, your attention goes there by which you

11:26.380 --> 11:33.310
become collectively conscious, or you can
say first you become just thoughtlessly aware.

11:33.310 --> 11:40.020
You are aware and you are thoughtlessly aware.
There is no thought because both the ego and

11:40.020 --> 11:42.310
superego are sucked in.

11:42.310 --> 11:47.550
When the kundalini pierces through this area,
the fontanelle bone area, I mean it’s a

11:47.550 --> 11:54.690
happening. It’s actualisation, it is not
just talking, giving your brain a washing,

11:54.690 --> 11:58.080
that you are all born realised and carry a
banner on your head

11:58.080 --> 12:03.780
‘born again, born again’ as you see many
people. I’m quite amazed at them, the way

12:03.780 --> 12:08.710
they talk. It’s surprising they go around
saying, oh we are already realised souls.

12:08.710 --> 12:14.860
I said how? How do you know? The kundalini
is frozen down there, you can see it so clearly.

12:14.860 --> 12:17.160
They say we are born again…self certified..

12:17.160 --> 12:22.300
You cannot get this certificate in any of
these colleges, you cannot have a course in

12:22.300 --> 12:27.250
this. It’s like sprouting of the seed, now
what course does sprouting of the seed have

12:27.250 --> 12:31.590
to do, poor thing. You just put it in the
Mother Earth and it sprouts, Mother Earth

12:31.590 --> 12:35.140
knows how to do it.

12:35.140 --> 12:43.100
Now this has to happen within us. Another
hurdle in all these western countries I’ve

12:43.100 --> 12:48.470
seen is this..why me? It’s a very common
question they ask, why you Mother, I say why

12:48.470 --> 12:50.820
not you? Better have it (Mother’s sweet
laughter)

12:50.820 --> 12:56.360
Better do it yourself, it would be a good
idea, you see I would like to retire, it’s

12:56.360 --> 13:02.160
a very good idea that you do it for me, and
you take my seat. As it is, I’m working

13:02.160 --> 13:07.060
very hard and sometimes my husband also gets
very upset with it. He said it’s too much

13:07.060 --> 13:11.920
you have to work very hard and one day he
put a question to some of the Sahaj Yogis,

13:11.920 --> 13:16.160
he said, now I don’t understand that when
She has given you realisation, why are you

13:16.160 --> 13:23.090
troubling her again and again? What’s the
matter with you? He is a man who has to deal

13:23.090 --> 13:30.260
with shipping and this girl said, Sir if there
are second hand ships you have to repair them

13:30.260 --> 13:34.350
again and again, but we are fifth hand ships,
so what to do?

13:34.350 --> 13:39.410
So, what I said was that this kind of foolish
attitude and stupid attitude is not going

13:39.410 --> 13:48.200
to help us. For example, this flame is burning,
do we ask the flame why do you burn and not

13:48.200 --> 13:53.670
these flowers? I mean, it’s somebody’s
quality, somebody’s nature, somebody’s

13:53.670 --> 13:58.700
gift or somebody’s speciality you can call
it.

13:58.700 --> 14:02.770
You could be doing this, I would be very happy
if you were doing this, really I tell you,

14:02.770 --> 14:07.000
I would have been very happy, but it is not
so. Now you know so many things, for example,

14:07.000 --> 14:12.390
you know driving. I don’t know, I don’t
even know how to sign a cheque, I’m so hopelessly

14:12.390 --> 14:17.240
bad in banks. I don’t know how to manage
money, I’m hopelessly bad in so many things,

14:17.240 --> 14:21.010
but I don’t feel bad about it in any way
because supposing I don’t know that, I know

14:21.010 --> 14:30.320
this. I can’t open the switch of an ordinary
tape recorder, but I can open the kundalini,

14:30.320 --> 14:35.230
it’s alright. It’s a different thing altogether
so why should you feel hurt? You cannot do

14:35.230 --> 14:39.080
each and every thing in the world can you?

14:39.080 --> 14:45.720
This kind of an attitude will make you unnecessarily
put a barrier for yourself, because this is

14:45.720 --> 14:52.360
your own, this is within you. I’m a gardener,
I’m doing nothing. I’m just like any enlightened

14:52.360 --> 14:56.390
light which is going to enlighten you so you
should quieten on this point. Please tell

14:56.390 --> 14:59.450
your mind to keep quiet on this point.

14:59.450 --> 15:11.890
(some communication from the hall re false
prophets)

15:11.890 --> 15:19.630
Nobody talks about them, I’m the only one
talking about them. Beware of them. False

15:19.630 --> 15:23.980
prophets are there but false prophets can
be known, can be understood but people don’t

15:23.980 --> 15:30.180
you see people go head long towards false
prophets. For example if somebody says that

15:30.180 --> 15:37.760
you are going to fly in the air and pay £3000
for that. Are you going to become birds? You

15:37.760 --> 15:44.120
use no brains and you just go straight forward
into it. There are people sitting here who

15:44.120 --> 15:52.910
have become insolvent because they tried to
fly with this guru, but the guru never flew.

15:52.910 --> 15:59.790
Now, how to make out a false prophet? The
thing is, you cannot pay for God I’m a happily

15:59.790 --> 16:07.400
married woman, quite well off, I mean I’m
really very happily married, but if I’m

16:07.400 --> 16:12.870
doing this work, I’m not taking any money
from you, nothing, you can’t pay for it.

16:12.870 --> 16:15.680
It’s something heavenly, this is the second
point.

16:15.680 --> 16:26.230
Thirdly…the third sign of a false prophet
is, what has he given you? Have you got your

16:26.230 --> 16:34.320
own powers? Can you feel your own powers?
That’s one of the greatest tests. If somebody

16:34.320 --> 16:42.120
says that oh my guru is great, he’s really
halfway to the lunatic asylum. A recluse and

16:42.120 --> 16:46.870
abnormal person. My guru has given me this
lunacy and I’ve paid so much money for that.

16:46.870 --> 16:51.500
So you ask a question to him, what has he
given you really? Can you feel the kundalini

16:51.500 --> 16:57.000
of this lady or this gentleman? Can you give
them realisation? Can you cure them? Can you

16:57.000 --> 17:03.890
understand where the problem is? Do you understand
where the problem is within you? Minimum of

17:03.890 --> 17:04.390
minimum!

17:04.390 --> 17:09.339
Supposing somebody says I’ve got my eyes
and he bumps into everything, will you call

17:09.339 --> 17:13.159
that person a person with eyes? You will definitely
say that he doesn’t want to believe that

17:13.159 --> 17:21.659
he is blind. It is exactly like this, you
must know that if it’s a true person, he

17:21.659 --> 17:26.149
will give you your own powers.

17:26.149 --> 17:38.970
(somebody speaking from the public) Mother’s
response:

17:38.970 --> 17:54.149
I wish you could meet somebody
who is here from Scotland, Peter..is he here?
You must meet him and you will know, it’s

17:54.149 --> 18:01.809
not only money, it’s much worse. I mean,
you have to decide. The other day, I had from

18:01.809 --> 18:05.539
Norwich, three prople who came to see me,
and they could not put their hands towards

18:05.539 --> 18:10.100
me, they kept going like this and like that
(possibly shaking). I was amazed and asked

18:10.100 --> 18:16.110
them, where have you been? They said we are
coming from a lunatic asylum. I said really?

18:16.110 --> 18:20.950
We are certified mad people, and where have
they been? To your great Mahashri!

18:20.950 --> 18:25.419
There is a lady in London (Mother asks yogis
if she has come…she was not there so Mother

18:25.419 --> 18:32.360
mentions all can meet. There is further sound
from the public to which Mother said ‘do

18:32.360 --> 18:39.460
not put me into controversy, better not discuss
these horrible people, that’s all I will

18:39.460 --> 18:42.490
say, forget them) Further comments from public..

18:42.490 --> 19:09.610
There are people who are suffering from epilepsy
and they

19:09.610 --> 19:16.230
come to me. They are falling, they have lost
all their wealth, their children are on the

19:16.230 --> 19:22.690
street, they come to me and they want to be
saved. I wish before talking about this, you

19:22.690 --> 19:26.919
better talk to those people who have come
to me and I have saved them. Not only saved

19:26.919 --> 19:36.320
them, but made something out of them. On the
contrary, this man has made them horrible.

19:36.320 --> 19:42.809
Many people who have been there have become
mad. This Mr Ben is suffering from a mysterious

19:42.809 --> 19:46.429
disease, from where did he get it? There is
one Dr Frenwick, you better go and meet him,

19:46.429 --> 19:51.580
he is finding out about this fellow, the way
he is giving epilepsy to many and I’ve cured

19:51.580 --> 19:56.909
the epilepsy of so many patients that he is
coming to me to know how I’ve cured them.

19:56.909 --> 20:04.549
Do you know what dangers you stand with these
people? You have no idea, you are so naïve.

20:04.549 --> 20:09.090
Did you ask him any questions? Please listen,
you have not come here to give lectures, please

20:09.090 --> 20:14.519
sit down, listen now. You have not come here
to ask questions, you are here to listen to

20:14.519 --> 20:19.850
me. Nobody asks questions to this dirty man,
never, they just pay him straight forward.

20:19.850 --> 20:26.149
Did they ask any questions to him? Ask this
gentleman or anyone. You just pray in silence,

20:26.149 --> 20:31.700
you are not even supposed to see this horrible
fellow, he is sitting in a dias somewhere.

20:31.700 --> 20:36.220
The way he has led his life, how dare you
compare me with him? You better go and stay

20:36.220 --> 20:40.679
with him. No! I’m just saying you have no
business to take advantage. You see, this

20:40.679 --> 20:45.870
is not proper, this is taking advantage of
my goodness, you dare not do these things.

20:45.870 --> 20:50.830
I don’t like it. It’s alright once in
a while, but not all the time. I have to talk

20:50.830 --> 20:54.720
something, you have come here to listen to
something, alright? Be sensible. (more noise

20:54.720 --> 21:00.610
from public) No, no you are not everything,
you are just thinking about yourself not others.

21:00.610 --> 21:04.909
You are not the only person sitting down here,
if you want to see me, come and see me privately

21:04.909 --> 21:08.409
alright? You have to be fair to others isn’t
it? They have come all the way to see me,

21:08.409 --> 21:13.940
some people have come from Torquay, you should
be more just and fair, I think you have not

21:13.940 --> 21:18.659
been fair to them. It’s alright once in
a while one question I answer but you are

21:18.659 --> 21:22.909
on and on and on, you must forget it. Listen
to me, it’s not you who is talking, I know

21:22.909 --> 21:26.389
who is talking behind it, it’s alright.

21:26.389 --> 21:34.240
Now the people do not say there are false
prophets, they never say and when Christ was

21:34.240 --> 21:42.370
asked, why do you criticise them? He said,
Satan is not going to speak against itself.

21:42.370 --> 21:50.120
They are not going to tell, they help each
other. They are the people who help each other,

21:50.120 --> 21:55.279
and you are so mesmerised by them that you
cannot see what wrong they are doing to you,

21:55.279 --> 21:59.509
until you reach that point where it’s all
finished.

21:59.509 --> 22:04.279
Now we have here (he has not come but will
be coming, you should meet him) a gentleman

22:04.279 --> 22:13.330
who has been with this man for the last sixteen
years. He has lost all his money, he has nothing,

22:13.330 --> 22:20.570
he was a diamond merchant his wife is a granddaughter
of a Duke, they are on the street. The wife

22:20.570 --> 22:26.720
used to get such horrible epilepsy, I cured
her. The child was screaming, you were not

22:26.720 --> 22:35.539
there, it’s easy to take a stand for somebody
who is satanic, at least don’t do that.

22:35.539 --> 22:41.360
You don’t know how people are harmed, everyday
I’m facing it, everyday I’m curing people.

22:41.360 --> 22:46.399
There are three people I know of who got cancer
out of this and tomorrow if anybody gets out

22:46.399 --> 22:52.730
of you, I’ll have to cure. He has taken
all the money, that’s all. I have every

22:52.730 --> 22:58.779
right to criticise them and say they are wrong,
because I’m the one who’s curing people,

22:58.779 --> 23:04.090
who are harmed by them, tortured by them.
I’m not saying just for fun sake, people

23:04.090 --> 23:08.789
have no courage to say also. How many have
courage to say that they are wrong and they

23:08.789 --> 23:13.610
have harmed? Very few people, they are cowards,
I would like to know how many people can say

23:13.610 --> 23:16.299
that openly that they are wrong, they have
harmed?

23:16.299 --> 23:20.340
There are some people sitting here, who have
been harmed who came to me and I have cured

23:20.340 --> 23:27.649
them. You need a lot of courage and understanding,
not only that but I am really angry with them

23:27.649 --> 23:33.340
because these are seekers of truth. These
are people seeking the truth and these people

23:33.340 --> 23:39.639
are not to be harmed by anyone. They are to
be given their realisation, they have to enter

23:39.639 --> 23:41.070
into the kingdom of God.

23:41.070 --> 23:47.580
God is anxiously waiting to give them what
they deserve. They are such great people,

23:47.580 --> 23:50.570
while these people (false gurus) wanted to
make money! They could have smuggled, they

23:50.570 --> 23:56.190
could have done other things, money is not
the only point but the way they have ruined

23:56.190 --> 24:01.419
the possibilities of their realisation! I
know of three others who are still in the

24:01.419 --> 24:06.350
lunatic asylum and I cannot save them. They
are all lost and the government doesn’t

24:06.350 --> 24:09.600
want to know anything about it. They went
and saw the police and the police said, what

24:09.600 --> 24:13.149
are we to do if you are fool and stupid people
who go ahead and spend your money and get

24:13.149 --> 24:16.619
these devils upon yourself?

24:16.619 --> 24:20.909
You must open your eyes and see for yourself
and see what is happening to your brothers

