Now the trouble is, in the west, people are
extremely naïve, absolutely naïve. They

27:25.539 --> 27:30.249
have no knowledge of the internal life, they
know about science as we are naïve about

27:30.249 --> 27:36.320
science you can say. We are naïve about the
lights and things in the banks maybe, but

27:36.320 --> 27:40.610
for the internal life you are absolutely naïve
and you do not know how many stratas there

27:40.610 --> 27:46.649
are within you. The first thing you must know
is that you live in the past and the future,

27:46.649 --> 27:49.830
not in the present.

27:49.830 --> 27:56.950
The past is the subconscious and the future
is the supraconscious. These two areas exist

27:56.950 --> 28:02.269
within us, within our body, one on the left
hand side and the other on the right hand

28:02.269 --> 28:08.529
side. When somebody contracts a disease like
say cancer, the attacks are from these areas.

28:08.529 --> 28:16.559
These areas are built within us from our creation.
