28:16.559 --> 28:22.320
These attacks come to us, for example even
a virus infection, even a possession that

28:22.320 --> 28:30.739
comes upon us, cancer, all these attacks come
to us, not because of our present, but because

28:30.739 --> 28:36.720
of our past. From somewhere, it attacks us.

28:36.720 --> 28:42.909
If you have to understand yourself, then you
must understand yourself in full perspective,

28:42.909 --> 28:46.350
not that somebody gives you a mantra and you
take the mantra for £300 and the meaning

28:46.350 --> 28:53.039
of the mantra is ‘I’m coming’ or some
