28:53.039 --> 29:00.580
You don’t know any Sanskrit. So these things
are put through in your subconscious and they

29:00.580 --> 29:07.289
work on you, and you feel a little bit relieved,
like with alcohol you may feel relieved for

29:07.289 --> 29:12.249
the time being. For the time being, you may
feel very elated and your ego will come up

29:12.249 --> 29:17.809
and you become a great person demanding this.
Like a man who was walking on the street,

29:17.809 --> 29:24.259
was drunk and the king was going on a horse.
He asked the king, I want to but this horse

29:24.259 --> 29:30.940
now get down from there. So the king said,
now you really want it? Alright, tomorrow.

29:30.940 --> 29:36.059
He went away. The king was a wise man. The
next day he called the fellow and said now

29:36.059 --> 29:40.340
do you want to buy the horse? He said ‘sir,
the one who was going to buy, is finished,

29:40.340 --> 29:43.779
he’s no more’. It’s like that.

29:43.779 --> 29:51.919
Suddenly, you see these subconscious spirits
or things that they possess you with, give

29:51.919 --> 29:59.340
you a very heightened ego, and the whole thing
fizzles out, but you do not know from where

29:59.340 --> 30:06.580
they come and where they go, you cannot understand
them and you cannot manoeuvre them. When you

30:06.580 --> 30:11.970
become yourself, you know each and every thing.
For example, this gentleman who was asking

30:11.970 --> 30:16.899
me questions, he does not know anything about
himself, neither about others. You ask any

30:16.899 --> 30:21.559
Sahaja yogi who is here, even a little child
will say what chakras are catching in him

30:21.559 --> 30:30.059
and what chakras are catching in you. It has
to be your own knowledge, in your own awareness,

30:30.059 --> 30:34.489
understand you are intelligent people, you
are not fools. I’m not talking to fools,

30:34.489 --> 30:40.629
I’m talking to intelligent people, who understand
things. If something has to happen to you,

30:40.629 --> 30:46.059
it has to happen in your awareness, like a
dog has a different awareness and you have

30:46.059 --> 30:52.200
a different awareness. You take any dog, even
if it is a pedigree dog, through any dirt

30:52.200 --> 30:55.629
or filth, it doesn’t smell, it doesn’t
feel bad, it doesn’t understand beauty,

30:55.629 --> 30:56.619
while you do.

30:56.619 --> 31:02.549
In the same way, something has to happen in
your awareness and that’s how you have to

31:02.549 --> 31:10.899
make it out. Unless and until that happens,
what’s the use? What’s the use of coming

31:10.899 --> 31:17.239
here? Just arguing with me, no use, you have
to get it. You have to get that within yourself.

31:17.239 --> 31:23.489
If that can happen within you, then only you
will be entitled as a self realised person,

31:23.489 --> 31:24.960
otherwise you will not.

31:24.960 --> 31:30.190
There is no organisation for them outside
because you are already organised by God.

31:30.190 --> 31:36.419
It’s all in there. Once it works out, you
start feeling it within you.

31:36.419 --> 31:41.779
Now, why people are false gurus? Let’s see
that point, then you will understand. First

31:41.779 --> 31:49.230
you must see the background of these people.
