31:55.119 --> 32:04.639
know. They don’t mind because he brings
lots of foreign exchange. Then there could

32:04.639 --> 32:11.239
be any thug or anybody in jail in India, who
comes out of the jail and has no place in

32:11.239 --> 32:18.450
society and comes to London and sits down
with funny dresses, with little horns around

32:18.450 --> 32:24.299
and all the British will be at his feet. Very
good idea!

32:24.299 --> 32:28.950
There should be no pretensions, if you are
true, there should be no pretensions about

32:28.950 --> 32:38.399
anything whatsoever. You should be straightforward
and normal, because you don’t want anything

32:38.399 --> 32:46.090
from anyone. I would say if I asked you to
stay with me without paying any amount or

32:46.090 --> 32:52.869
any money, you would not accept such a situation.
