32:52.869 --> 32:58.090
parasites, of the worst type. They live on
your money.

32:58.090 --> 33:03.480
Christ was the son of a carpenter, he didn’t
ask for money from anyone, did he? He did

33:03.480 --> 33:11.470
the carpenters job. You can’t understand
it because it’s the ego, it’s a very subtle

33:11.470 --> 33:22.940
ego that you have purchased your guru. You
cannot purchase Me. You cannot purchase your

33:22.940 --> 33:29.080
realisation, God doesn’t understand money,
