34:08.530 --> 34:19.700
which are universal in our dreams. He has
proved it. If so, then that collective unconscious

34:19.700 --> 34:23.730
within us has to become conscious within us.

34:23.730 --> 34:30.500
This is what any true Prophet will tell you.
He will not give you a thing that you have

34:30.500 --> 34:36.100
to jump all the time or that you have to take
out your clothes or stand on your head, because

34:36.100 --> 34:41.510
it is very simple to understand that by doing
any effort you are not going to go to God.

34:41.510 --> 34:46.140
By doing anything you are not going to do.
