35:00.420 --> 35:06.350
any effort, because it is so vital, it is
so important. You do not understand the importance

35:06.350 --> 35:13.500
of that, you want to play about with all nonsensical
things. The most vital thing today is to evolve

35:13.500 --> 35:21.370
and this evolution must take place, and this
takes place within us because a system has

35:21.370 --> 35:26.830
been built within us already, it exists within
us and you can see with your naked eyes the

35:26.830 --> 35:32.480
rising of the kundalini, the breaking of the
Sahasrara, the breaking of the fontanelle

35:32.480 --> 35:41.780
bone area which is the real actual Baptism.
