38:56.270 --> 39:03.100
job, that’s not the way I am. I’m a different
type, absolutely different and this is the

39:03.100 --> 39:12.030
type always has been denied, not today, always.
Why Christ was denied? For what? All of them

39:12.030 --> 39:23.080
were denied and all the false were accepted.
