40:00.410 --> 40:05.610
last judgement has started, this is the last
judgement. How God is going to judge you?

40:05.610 --> 40:09.110
Just think of it, is He going to judge you
the way you are educated? The way you are

40:09.110 --> 40:16.180
dressed? No. Through your inner happening,
through your inner understanding and light

40:16.180 --> 40:22.220
that is within you. That’s how he is going
to judge you. I’m here to give you light

40:22.220 --> 40:28.460
that is your own, just an enlightened light
enlightens you. I don’t want to pamper your

40:28.460 --> 40:34.210
ego or to run you down but I want to tell
you that you should become yourself. I see

40:34.210 --> 40:38.800
the beauty within you, I see that diamond
within you, that’s why I’m doing all this

40:38.800 --> 40:43.010
work. You do not see it, I just want you to
feel it and have it, it’s a very simple

40:43.010 --> 40:48.800
thing. What is there to be so much worried
about? To talk about other people who have

40:48.800 --> 40:54.170
done nothing, there are 90,000 people doing
