41:50.080 --> 41:55.470
they have got their circuses, they have got
big (unclear) all things to announce themselves

41:55.470 --> 41:59.470
and people think they must be great people.

41:59.470 --> 42:05.030
Christ was a simple man, wasn’t he? He was
